articles.author: By Sarah Dean and Lauren Kent, CNN
articles.title: UK to add Germany, Austria, several other European countries to 'green' travel list - CNN
articles.description: The UK government will update its "green" travel list on Thursday to add Germany, Austria, Slovenia, Slovakia, Latvia, Romania, and Norway to the list.
articles.content:
London (CNN) The UK government will update its "green" travel list on Thursday to add Germany, Austria, Slovenia, Slovakia, Latvia, Romania, and Norway to the list.
